{"tid":2219741,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新移民爭遞表申1萬元爆混亂","createTime":"2020-09-27T05:59:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T07:59:50.000Z","uid":163493,"like":16,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"7115ea4422237a0765726f91ed64ad765e89fbfa","tid":2219741,"uid":163493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T05:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/xtImjAAam1SPBvHr2ZR3TA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-09/01d273d0-0082-11eb-afff-9f9e1c04c33a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FxtImjAAam1SPBvHr2ZR3TA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-09%2F01d273d0-0082-11eb-afff-9f9e1c04c33a&h=8973b110&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ndllm<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f99f8c0a3843e62600d975826df17149a9dfc0","tid":2219741,"uid":163493,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:02:09.000Z","msg":"港府早前宣布透過關愛基金「補鑊」，向來自低收入家庭的新來港定居成員發放1萬港元津貼，首批合資格人士(1971年或之前出生)，可於今(27日)起遞交申請，需時約8周，即最快11月下旬才獲發津貼。有到場遞表的新移民指出，長者難以自行準備入息證明等文件，不滿計劃設有經濟審查，認為應惠及所有長者。及至約10時，勞工及福利局局長羅致光到場視察，並與現場職員談話，逗留約20分鐘離去，期間未有回應記者提問。<br />\n<br />\n位於深水埗的中銀香港分行，接近9時有約30名市民於分行外排隊，等候索取或遞交申請表格。其後分行開門營業，眾人爭相入場，場面一度發生混亂，須分行職員調停。<br />\n<br />\n排頭位的伍先生指出，因「開心有錢攞」，特地提早1小時排隊，冀能盡早取得津貼。他指，已退休2年，靠每月5000多港元綜援過活，惟劏房租金及水電費已花去約3000港元，每日開支須維持在90港元內。他稱，疫情下口罩價格昂貴，無力負擔，只能重複使用4至5日，惟他現正輪候公屋，故不會把款項用以購買防疫物資，打算儲起留待裝修公屋之用。<br />\n<br />\n來港定居約4年、約80歲的關先生指出，家中僅靠任職清潔工的太太支撐，月薪約1萬港元，扣除屋租等雜費，每月僅剩下約6000港元，料會儲起津貼以備不時之需。他又指，計劃要求申請人填寫大量文件，對長者而言有一定困難，認為港府不應審查長者經濟情況，直指「咁審查法不如唔好畀(津貼)」。<br />\n<br />\n任職泥水工人的秦先生則指，疫情下工作量大減，收入跌約一半，加上他不諳廣東話，難以找到其他工作，只能暫以積蓄支付租金等日常開支，財政壓力大增。他指，不會揮霍該筆津貼，打算用作補貼生活開支，料足以支付約2個月租金。"},{"pid":"49f62bb0579b52f69c75d3758850194068b0ec29","tid":2219741,"uid":343361,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:02:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e45aa721ae8ae9bff0fcac0777cf9475d1eb966","tid":2219741,"uid":76470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:04:06.000Z","msg":"新移民續個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c3e0f56950a9a7c0df08bf8fbfed6f3723962fa","tid":2219741,"uid":111322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:04:28.000Z","msg":"派多d 丫嘛"},{"pid":"d746f96370ca045601730078fdd911cda1e51b89","tid":2219741,"uid":348947,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:04:52.000Z","msg":"唔係呀80歲都可以係四年前嚟香港"},{"pid":"e3c557ae0f22fcdd9a75cb938aeabfd160c0068e","tid":2219741,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d746f96370ca045601730078fdd911cda1e51b89","tid":2219741,"uid":348947,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:04:52.000Z","msg":"唔係呀80歲都可以係四年前嚟香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd361f01deb6faf6f38ac399465eeb9fc00e1382","tid":2219741,"uid":181581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:06:43.000Z","msg":"第四波疫情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80203d775d2232f9c9980d6eeb08584a59accee3","tid":2219741,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:07:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f932abe9e447b3d78e59db5552127b216257886c","tid":2219741,"uid":301952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"